 <br />
....................... SOE need to put more effort into making Norrath a relivable world. Players have to have a reason to explore that old content, and to be that community a new player can join, beyond the transient urge to try out another character. With a solid effort at giving new players the game every role-playing MMORPG promises- a dynamic world in which you can meet friends and explore the world- EverQuest can pull out of the holding pattern it is in and introduce a whole new breed of players to Norrath.</div>
			
